resourceAbstractObject.default: Data from the 'Monitoring pollination in the Mediterranean region' (POLLIMED): Monitoring pollination in the Mediterranean region. This observatory is part of the Montpellier Research Observatory of Environment (OSU OREME, oreme.org). It consists in different observing tasks: Communities of pollinating insects ; Olive tree pollination ; Plant-pollinator chemical communication ; Pollen-vegetation-climate relationships ; Vine pollination.
